eq 2^{2012} \cdot 3$. So $2^{2014}-2^{2012} 
mid 2^{2014}+2^{2012}$. So the fraction cannot be simplified into an integer. Hence the answer is the only fraction, $ oxed{	extbf{(C)}}$.
